%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Activist%20Dabholkar%20murder%20case%3A%202%20get%20life%20in%20prison%2C%203%20acquitted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715321274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110000419%2Cimgsize-19812.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Factivist-narendra-dabholkar-murder-case-2-get-life-imprisonment-3-acquitted%2Farticleshow%2F110000459.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Pune%20court%20on%20Friday%20found%20two%20accused%20guilty%20in%202013%20murder%20case%20of%20activist%20Narendra%20Dabholkar.%20The%20two%20were%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%20Activist%20Narendra%20Dabholkar%20was%20shot%20in%20Pune%20on%20August%2020%2C%202013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Just%20Slow%20Down%E2%80%99%3A%20Couple%20Quit%20City%20Life%20to%20Build%20Bamboo%20Homestay%20Surrounded%20by%20Nature%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20sound%20of%20crickets%20chirping%2C%20the%20sun%20peeking%20through%20the%20dense%20foliage%2C%20and%20the%20distant%20mooing%20of%20cows%20in%20the%20nearby%20farmland%20create%20a%20serene%20backdrop%20as%20you%20sit%20on%20the%20porch%20of%20a%20mud%20house.%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20that%20all%20sound%20like%20a%20dreamy%20break%20from%20the%20harsh%20city%20noises%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20my%20childhood%2C%20this%20picture-perfect%20dream%20was%20my%20life%20during%20the%20summer%20vacations.%20With%20my%20tummy%20full%20of%20delicious%20meals%2C%20I%20would%20simply%20enjoy%20spending%20my%20time%20exploring%20the%20farms%20near%20my%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20home%20with%20my%20little%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20all%20of%20this%20might%20sound%20like%20a%20far-fetched%20idea%20to%20you%2C%20there%20is%20a%20quaint%20home%20nestled%20in%20the%20sleepy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320476%2Fhistory-and-origin-of-chhurpi-worlds-hardest-cheese-northeast-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etown%20of%20Kalimpong%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20promises%20all%20this%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPalighar%20is%20steeped%20in%20tradition%20and%20authentic%20rustic%20life.%20It%20is%20a%20two%20bedroom%20homestay%20where%20we%20try%20to%20connect%20our%20guests%20with%20the%20local%20culture%2C%20food%2C%20flora%20and%20fauna%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ahana%20Gurung%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Palighar%20Homestay%20tells%20The%3Cstrong%3E%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReturning%20to%20the%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kalimpong%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20couple%20running%20the%20homestay%2C%20Ahana%20and%20Kabir%2C%20were%20childhood%20friends.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20moved%20to%20different%20cities%20for%20our%20education%20and%20job%20but%20we%20longed%20for%20our%20home.%20That%20longing%20brought%20us%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kabir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20shares%20how%20in%20the%20small%20hill%20station%2C%20with%20fewer%20work%20opportunities%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20of%20the%20talent%20moves%20out.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorking%20outside%20is%20a%20common%20trend%20and%20the%20people%20from%20our%20generation%20never%20really%20come%20back%20home.%20Kabir%20and%20I%20always%20had%20this%20idea%2C%20that%20we%20would%20come%20home%20and%20do%20something%20that%20would%20employ%20more%20local%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kabir%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344999%2Fhomestay-in-panchgani-roadtrip-from-mumbai-sustainable-organic-food-solar-panel-long-weekend-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarting%20a%20homestay%20%3C%2Fa%3Eseemed%20like%20a%20natural%20path.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20959px)%20100vw%2C%20959px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22959%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kabir%20and%20Ahana%20moved%20back%20to%20Kalimpong%20to%20build%20homestay%20of%20their%20dreams.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085.jpg%20959w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085-768x577.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349520%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKabir%20and%20Ahana%20moved%20back%20to%20Kalimpong%20to%20build%20homestay%20of%20their%20dreams.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20ancestral%20land%20and%20farms%20that%20I%20utilised%20to%20make%20a%20farm%20stay%20and%20give%20people%20a%20peek%20into%20the%20culture%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20from%20the%20city%20to%20his%20homeland%20was%20a%20decision%20of%20a%20lifetime.%20Kabir%20took%20the%20leap%20in%202016%2C%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20moved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20move%20was%20soon%20followed%20by%20Ahana%20in%202020.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20have%20ancestral%20land%20in%20a%20great%20location%20to%20begin%20with.%20While%20Kabir%20worked%20on%20building%20the%20property%2C%20I%20worked%20remotely%20to%20market%20the%20property%20before%20finally%20moving%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Palighar%20opened%20its%20gates%20to%20its%20first%20guests.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20homestay%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20happy%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESteeped%20in%20tradition%20and%20sustainability%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalighar%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20homestay%20that%20smells%20of%20customs%20and%20traditions%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20luxury%20and%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20homestay%20gives%20the%20guests%20is%20an%20authentic%20escape%20from%20their%20city%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKabir%20shares%20that%20growing%20up%2C%20he%20noticed%20how%20the%20houses%20in%20the%20area%20were%20being%20modernised.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20old-school%20mud%20homes%20with%20sloping%20bamboo%20roofs%2C%20which%20were%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20area%2C%20were%20all%20gone.%20In%20losing%20our%20traditional%20architecture%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20losing%20the%20customs%20and%20traditions%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20preserve%20the%20traditional%20culture%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20use%20a%20traditional%20technique%20called%20Irka%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20%E2%80%9CEssentially%2C%20what%20the%20technique%20involves%20is%20using%20bamboo%2C%20wood%20and%20mud%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20The%20mud%2C%20mixed%20with%20dung%20and%20straw%2C%20is%20plastered%20on%20a%20wooden%20frame%20woven%20with%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Karan%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20made%20mud%20bricks%20which%20are%20baked%20in%20the%20sun.%20We%20used%20the%20land%20from%20our%20own%20property%20which%20helped%20us%20reduce%20our%20carbon%20footprint.%20We%20were%20really%20conscious%20of%20the%20impact%20we%20have%20on%20the%20nature%20around%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Ahana%20also%20points%20out%20that%20another%20reason%20to%20use%20mud%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20natural%20coolant.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20temperatures%20in%20these%20areas%20have%20typically%20been%20low%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20hotter%20days%20now.%20We%20wanted%20to%20use%20a%20method%20that%20keeps%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally%20which%20is%20why%20we%20used%20mud%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20588px)%20100vw%2C%20588px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20place%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20riverside%20where%20you%20can%20enjoy%20picnic%20with%20your%20family.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113.jpg%20588w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349522%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22441%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20place%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20riverside%20where%20you%20can%20enjoy%20picnic%20with%20your%20family.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20currently%20has%20two%20ensuite%20rooms%20and%20a%20common%20dining%20area.%20The%20property%20is%20located%20on%203.5%20acres%20of%20paddy%20and%20maize%20fields.%20It%20offers%20scenic%20outdoors%20with%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20mountain%20farm%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20multiple%20lawns%20for%20you%20to%20take%20walks%20in%20and%20a%20gazebo-style%20seating%20area%20where%20you%20can%20sip%20delicious%20Darjeeling%20tea%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kabir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20made%20with%20natural%20materials%2C%20the%20homestay%20also%20follows%20an%20eco-friendly%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20minimise%20the%20use%20of%20practice.%20We%20encourage%20our%20guests%20not%20to%20bring%20their%20own%20water%20as%20we%20provide%20them%20with%20filtered%20water%20over%20bottled%20water.%20We%20also%20compost%20all%20our%20kitchen%20waste%20and%20leaves.%20This%20compost%20eventually%20goes%20back%20to%20our%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kabir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shows%20the%20process%20of%20mulching%20and%20composting%20to%20the%20guests%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20is%20also%20a%20haven%20for%20bird%20watchers%20and%20nature%20lovers.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20seven%20years%2C%20we%20have%20tried%20to%20make%20a%20habitat%20for%20butterflies%2C%20insects%20and%20birds.%20We%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20insects%20and%20birds%20flocking%20in%20the%20area%20such%20as%20Rent%20Vented%20Bulbul%2C%20Common%20Tailorbird%2C%20Gray%20Treepie%20etc%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spend%2048%20hours%20at%20Palighar%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20spending%20your%20time%20admiring%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290101%2Fbest-homestay-in-himachal-pradesh-sainj-valley-eco-friendly-kath-k