20that%20she%20died%20instantly%20upon%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20still%20don't%20know%20precisely%20what%20may%20have%20happened.%20I%20am%20shocked%20and%20in%20disbelief%2C%26quot%3B%20Matteo%20Sanguineti%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Fly%20Emotion%20company%2C%20told%20Italian%20news%20outlet%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETODAYNews%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20the%20complete%20disposal%20of%20the%20judiciary%20which%20is%20now%20investigating.%20And%20we%20are%20close%20to%20the%20victim's%20family.%20Over%20200%20thousand%20people%20will%20have%20flown%20on%20the%20crossing%20between%20the%20towns%20of%20Bema%20and%20Albaredo.%20I%20am%20shocked%20and%20incredulous%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sanguineti%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moutahir's%20two%20nieces%20were%20with%20her%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20tragedy.%20They%20filmed%20the%20entire%20incident%20while%20completing%20the%20zipline%20course%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fboy-9-saves-parents-after-oklahoma-tornado-tosses-car-please-dont-die-i-will-be-back-5624103%5C%22%3EBoy%2C%209%2C%20Saves%20Parents%20After%20US%20Tornado%20Tosses%20Car%3A%20%26quot%3BPlease%20Don't%20Die%2C%20I%20Will%20Be%20Back%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20that%20the%2041-year-old%20stopped%20on%20the%20steel%20cable%20and%20was%20suspended%20in%20the%20air%20for%20several%20seconds.%20Cops%20believe%20that%20she%20likely%20%26quot%3Bbegan%20to%20struggle%26quot%3B%20after%20realising%20she%20had%20stopped.%20%26quot%3BThis%20led%20to%20her%20becoming%20unbalanced%20and%20she%20fell%20from%20the%20harness%20around%2020m%20into%20the%20forest%20below%20and%20was%20killed%20instantly%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20possible%20she%20had%20some%20sort%20of%20panic%20attack%20and%20that's%20what%20made%20her%20struggle%20or%20maybe%20s