gone%20into%20the%20project%20-%20cinematographer%20Pratham%20Mehta%20and%20editors%20Debasmita%20Mitra%20and%20Sanjay%20Sankla%20do%20their%20jobs%20to%20perfection%20-%20does%20not%20overshadow%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20congenitally%20sightless%20hero%20fights%20seemingly%20insurmountable%20odds%2C%20including%20widespread%20discrimination%2C%20dispiriting%20bullying%20and%20a%20myopic%20education%20system%20that%20has%20no%20scope%20for%20differently%20abled%20people%20to%20go%20in%20for%20higher%20studies%20in%20the%20field%20of%20science%20even%20if%20they%20score%20the%20requisite%20grades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarring%20a%20somewhat%20shrill%20opening%20sequence%20that%20over-dramatizes%20the%20circumstances%20and%20the%20immediate%20repercussions%20of%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20blind%20boy%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Machilipatnam%20in%20then%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20screenplay%20by%20Jagdeep%20Siddhu%20and%20Sumit%20Purohit%20steers%20well%20clear%20of%20overly%20maudlin%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20pivotal%20courtroom%20scenes%20in%20which%20Srikanth%2C%20with%20teacher%20Devika%20(Jy0thika)%20steadfastly%20by%20his%20side%2C%20has%20to%20convince%20a%20judge%2C%20a%20college%20principal%20and%20a%20skeptical%20lawyer%20that%20he%20deserves%20a%20fair%20shot%2C%20the%20film%20devises%20ways%20not%20to%20undermine%20its%20moderate%20tonal%20qualities%20even%20as%20it%20makes%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20individuals%20with%20physical%20abnormalities%20to%20be%20given%20equal%20opportunities.Admittedly%2C%20on%20a%20few%20occasions%20-%20one%20of%20them%20centres%20on%20a%20harrowing%20moment%20in%20which%20Srikanth's%20father%20digs%20a%20pit%20early%20in%20the%20film%2C%20an%20act%20that%20he%20repeats%20much%20later%20in%20a%20completely%20altered%20context%20-%20the%20film%20tends%20to%20state%20the%20obvious%20when%20you%20expect%20it%20to%20leave%20something%20to%20the%20imagination%20and%20the%20interpretative%20faculties%20of%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ESrikanth%3C%2Fi%3E%20tells%20the%20remarkable%20story%20of%20a%20young%20man%20endowed%20with%20exceptional%20vision%20and%20tenacity%20but%20does%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20pointing%20to%20the%20delicate%20junctures%20in%20Srikanth%20Bolla's%20life%20when%20he%20comes%20precariously%20close%20to%20letting%20his%20self-confidence%20turn%20into%20a%20degree%20of%20arrogance%20and%20success%20into%20streaks%20of%20insouciance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20moments%20of%20weakness%20trigger%20friction%20with%20the%20handful%20of%20key%20people%20in%20his%20life%2C%20including%20his%20girlfriend%20Swathi%20(Alaya%20F)%2C%20a%20medical%20student%20who%20connects%20with%20him%20on%20social%20media%20before%20meeting%20him%20in%20person%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%2C%20where%20Srikanth%20enrolls%20as%20a%20full%20scholarship%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FOMeuJP5iBWY%3Fsi%3DWxN--_PFV6ZwZG1-%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20crafts%20an%20engaging%20portrait%20of%20a%20man%20whose%20single-minded%20pursuit%20of%20his%20own%20goals%20and%20a%20plan%20to%20help%20other%20physically%20challenged%20and%20economically%20disadvantaged%20people%20find%20a%20firm%20footing%20in%20life%2C%20it%20also%20acknowledges%20the%20chinks%20in%20the%20man's%20armour%20that%20threaten%20to%20push%20his%20true%20well-wishers%20away%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ESrikanth%3C%2Fi%3E%20uses%20the%20%3Ci%3EQayamat%20Se%20Qayamat%3C%2Fi%3E%20song%20%3Ci%3EPapa%20kehte%20hai%20bada%20naam%20karega%20beta%20hamara%20aisa%20kaam%20karega%3C%2Fi%3E%20as%20a%20musical%20refrain%20but%20it%20does%20not%20focus%20so%20much%20on%20the%20hero's%20father%20as%20on%20a%20teacher%20who%20takes%20the%20boy%20under%20her%20wings%20and%20teaches%20him%20how%20to%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20adversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20teacher%20Devika%20is%20the%20anchor%20who%20gives%20Srikanth%20the%20freedom%20to%20dream%2C%20investor%20and%20friend%20Ravi%20(Sharad%20Kelkar)%20is%20the%20man%20who%20believes%20in%20the%20protagonist's%20aspiration%20to%20own%20and%20run%20a%20business%20of%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ESrikanth%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20not%20given%20to%20saying%20sorry%2C%20but%20he%20does%20say%20thank%20you%20either%20in%20so%20many%20words.%20Of%20course%2C%20he%20delivers%20an%20entire%20soliloquy%20that%20acknowledges%20his%20supporters%20and%20his%20own%20fierce%20sense%20of%20self-worth.%20The%20contradictory%20impulses%20within%20him%20are%20perfectly%20understandable%20given%20that%20he%20has%20never%20had%20anything%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20passage%20of%20the%20film%20revolves%20around%20the%20then%20President%20of%20India%20A.P.J.%20Abdul%20Kalam%20and%20his%20%26quot%3BLead%20India%26quot%3B%20campaign%2C%20which%20inspires%20%3Ci%3ESrikanth%3C%2Fi%3E%20to%20redouble%20his%20efforts%20to%20achieve%20what%20his%20heart%20desires.%20However%2C%20an%20encounter%20with%20a%20self-seeking%20politician%20leaves%20him%20disillusioned%20and%20teaches%20him%20a%20lesson%20or%20two%20about%20the%20pitfalls%20of%20short-cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ability%20to%20'see'%20without%20one's%20eyes%20is%20the%20most%20important%20element%20in%20the%20%3Ci%3ESrikanth%3C%2Fi%3E%20story.%20It%20is%20what%20sets%20him%20apart.%20Main%20sirf%20sapna%20hi%20dekh%20sakta%20hoon%20(I%20can%20see%20only%20in%20my%20dreams)%20is%20a%20line%20that%20he%20delivers%20more%20than%20once.%20Dream%20big%2C%20he%20keeps%20insisting%20when%20Ravi%20tries%20to%20rein%20him%20in%20with%20his%20reality%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Srikanth%20is%20also%20a%20man%20of%20action.%20He%20goes%20from%20%3Ci%3EMain%20sab%20kuch%20kar%20sakta%20hoon%3C%2Fi%3E%20(I%20can%20do%20everything)%20to%20%3Ci%3EMain%20kuch%20bhi%20kar%20sakta%20hoon%3C%2Fi%3E%20(I%20can%20do%20anything).%20The%20former%20is%20an%20assertion%20of%20intent%3B%20the%20latter%20has%20the%20ring%20of%20a%20warning.%20The%20character%20becomes%20all%20the%20more%20relatable%20because%20of%20the%20inner%20pulls%20and%20pressures%20that%20he%20encounters%20as%20he%20deals%20with%20challenges%20from%20within%20and%20without.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajkummar%20Rao%20plays%20Srikanth%20from%20roughly%20the%20age%20of%2014%20-%20that%20is%20how%20old%20the%20Bollant%20Industries%20founder%20was%20when%20he%20first%20met%20President%20Abdul%20Kalam%20-%20to%20about%20his%20mid-20s.%20It%20obviously%20isn't%20easy%20for%20the%20actor%20to%20pass%20himself%20off%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20but%20he%20delivers%20a%20performance%20that%20is%20so%20convincing%20and%20nuanced%20on%20all%20other%20counts%20-%20the%20physical%20impairment%2C%20the%20dialogue%20delivery%2C%20the%20body%20language%20-%20that%20one%20cannot%20but%20marvel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20actor%20has%20exceptional%20support%20from%20Jyothika%20and%20Sharad%20Kelkar%20-%20both%20are%20epitomes%20of%20restraint%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20sustained%20balanced%20timbre%20of%20the%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ESrikanth%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20as%20uplifting%20a%20film%20as%20any%2C%20deserves%20a%20wide%20audience.%20It%20is%20more%20than%20a%20mere%20story.%20It%20is%20a%20heartwarming%20celebration%20of%20a%20way%20of%20seeing%20the%20world%20in%20a%20new%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715313840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvi4l9d4o_srikanth_625x300_10_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsrikanth-review-aided-by-rajkummar-raos-skilful-performance-this-is-no-ordinary-bollywood-biop