tent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeparatist%20and%20%26quot%3BWaris%20Punjab%20De%26quot%3B%20chief%20Amritpal%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20Assam's%20Dibrugarh%20Jail%2C%20approached%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20on%20Friday%20seeking%20temporary%20release%20to%20file%20his%20nomination%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20separatist%20Sikh%20preacher%20plans%20to%20contest%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate%20from%20Punjab's%20Sri%20Khadoor%20Sahib%20constituency%20that%20goes%20to%20poll%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Singh%20sought%20an%20order%20to%20be%20released%20for%20seven%20days%20so%20he%20could%20file%20his%20nomination%20for%20the%20polls%20before%20the%20deadline%20ends%20on%20May%2014.%20He%20has%20also%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20jail%20authorities%20to%20make%20necessary%20arrangements%20for%20him%20to%20complete%20the%20paperwork%20including%20getting%20his%20photograph%20clicked%20and%20opening%20a%20new%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioner%20is%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%20and%20an%20elector%20from%20Khadoor%20Sahib%20Constituency%20and%20therefore%20is%20qualified%20for%20contesting%20the%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20also%20mentions%20that%20Singh's%20father%20Tarsem%20Singh%20has%20written%20letters%20to%20Punjab's%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20as%20well%20as%20Amritsar's%20District%20Magistrate%20to%20provide%20guidelines%20for%20him%20to%20file%20his%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20in%20his%20petition%2C%20alleged%20that%20even%20though%20the%20Punjab%20poll%20chief%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20seeking%20necessary%20action%20to%20facilitate%20his%20nomination%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BState%20of%20Punjab%20and%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20Amritsar%20have%20deliberately%20not%20issued%20any%20further%20instructions%20in%20order%20to%20delay%20and%20ma