%20cause%20blood%20clots%20in%20rare%20cases%2C%20a%20group%20of%20doctors%20on%20Thursday%20expressed%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20Covishield%20vaccine%20manufactured%20by%20the%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20doctors%2C%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20Awaken%20India%20Movement%20(AIM)%2C%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20review%20the%20science%20behind%20all%20Covid%20vaccines%20and%20audit%20their%20commercialisation%20as%20well%20as%20implementation%20of%20active%20surveillance%20and%20monitoring%20mechanism%20to%20ensure%20vaccine%20adverse%20events%20are%20identified%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20wholly%20ignored%20the%20rising%20number%20of%20cases%20of%20tragic%20deaths%20post-Covid%20vaccination%20all%20the%20while%20and%20continues%20to%20promote%20Covid%20vaccines%20as%20'safe%20and%20effective'%2C%20without%20scientific%20investigation%20and%20invoking%20epidemiology%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Tarun%20Kothari%2C%20a%20radiologist%20and%20an%20activist%2C%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20is%20learning%20about%20a%20side%20effect%20of%20the%20Covid%20vaccine%20called%20Thrombosis%20with%20Thrombocytopenia%20Syndrome%20(TTS)%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20COVID-19%20vaccines%20were%20being%20administered%2C%20not%20many%20people%20were%20aware%20that%20it%20was%20being%20done%20without%20the%20completion%20of%20phase-3%20trials.%20Administration%20of%20COVID-19%20vaccines%20was%20started%20without%20the%20manufacturers%20having%20complete%20information%20and%20data%20on%20the%20possible%20short-term%20or%20long-term%20side%20effects%2C%20or%20fatalities%2C%20said%20Dr%20Sujata%20Mittal%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20oncologist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20already%20low%20awareness%20around%20vaccine%20injuries%2C%20especially%20in%20India%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20women%20reported%20abnormalities%20in%20their%20menstrual%20cycles%2C%20which%20was%20confirmed%20much%20later%20as%20a%20side%20effect%20of%20the%20vaccine%20in%20a%20study%20published%20in%20September%202022%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Awaken%20India%20Movement%20(AIM)%20has%20been%20collecting%20details%20of%20Covid%20Vaccine%20deaths%20covered%20by%20media%2Fsocial%20media%20in%20India%20and%20sharing%20them%20with%20various%20high%20authorities%20of%20the%20country%20since%202021%2C%20when%20the%20vaccination%20began.%20The%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20respond%20to%20our%20repeated%20requests%20to%20investigate%20deaths%20and%20debilitation%20from%20adverse%20effects%20of%20vaccination%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kothari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM%20urged%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20compensate%20all%20the%20victims%20of%20Covid%20vaccines%2C%20including%20their%20family%20members%2C%20through%20a%20mechanism%20that%20involves%20vaccine%20manufacturers%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20demand%20establishing%20fast%20track%20courts%20and%20vaccine%20courts%20to%20provide%20swift%20justice%20to%20the%20vaccine%20injured%20and%20their%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Mittal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20active%20surveillance%20and%20monitoring%20mechanisms%20should%20be%20implemented%20to%20ensure%20vaccine%20adverse%20events%20are%20identified%20as%20early%20as%20possible%20and%20early%20treatment%20protocols%20must%20be%20created%20and%20widely%20publicised%20so%20that%20lives%20can%20be%20saved%2C%20she%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReview%20science%20behind%20all%20Covid%20vaccines%20and%20audit%20their%20commercialisation%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kothari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Kingdom-based%20AstraZeneca%20has%20started%20global%20withdrawal%20of%20its%20COVID-19%20vaccine%2C%20which%20was%20provided%20in%20India%20as%20'Covishield'%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India%2C%20days%20after%20it%20admitted%20to%20rare%20side%20effects%20of%20blood%20clotting%20and%20lowering%20of%20platelet%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20withdrawal%20has%20been%20initiated%20due%20to%20a%20surplus%20of%20available%20updated%20vaccines%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20company's%20partner%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India%20said%20it%20has%20stopped%20the%20manufacturing%20and%20supply%20of%20additional%20doses%20of%20Covishield%20since%20December%202021%20while%20reiterating%20that%20it%20had%20disclosed%20all%20rare%20to%20very%20rare%20side%20effects%2C%20including%20TTS%2C%20in%20the%20packaging%20insert%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstraZeneca%20had%20partnered%20with%20Oxford%20University%20to%20develop%20the%20COVID-19%20vaccine%2C%20which%20was%20sold%20as%20Vaxzevria%20in%20Europe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715312520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2F9fh3h5is_covishield-covid-vaccine-pti_625x300_27_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovishield-side-effects-doctors-group-urges-centre-to-review-all-covid-vaccines-5626724%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20wake%20of%20pharmaceutical%20giant%20AstraZeneca%20admitting%20in%20a%20UK%20court%20that%20its%20Covid%20vaccine%20can%20cause%20blood%20clots%20in%20rare%20cases%2C%20a%20group%20of%20doctors%20on%20Thursday%20expressed%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20Covishield%20vaccine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovishield-side-effects-doctors-group-urges-centre-to