uch%20was%20a%20urologist%2C%20who%20specialized%20in%20infertility%20and%20male%20reproductive%20health.%C2%A0The%20outlet%20reported%20that%20he%20carried%20out%20the%20abuse%20from%202015%20through%202019%20when%20he%20was%20alone%20with%20his%20patients%20in%20the%20exam%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20said%20he%20used%20to%C2%A0allegedly%20instruct%20his%20victims%20to%20masturbate%20themselves.%20He%20also%20used%20sex%20toys%20on%20them%20and%20carried%20out%20unnecessary%20rectal%20exams%20without%20wearing%20gloves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Manhattan%20US%20Attorney's%20Office%2C%20the%2055-year-old%20doctor%20was%20found%20guilty%20by%20a%20jury%20Wednesday%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20on%20all%2013%20counts%20he%20faced%20related%20to%20his%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20eight%20patients.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Fstatement-us-attorney-damian-williams-conviction-darius-paduch%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20U.S.%20Attorney%20Damian%20Williams%20said%2C%20''As%20a%20unanimous%20jury%20has%20just%20found%2C%20Darius%20A.%20Paduch%20leveraged%20his%20position%20of%20trust%20as%20a%20medical%20doctor%20for%20his%20perverse%20gratification.%20For%20years%2C%20patients%20seeking%20needed%20medical%20care%2C%20many%20of%20them%20children%2C%20left%20his%20office%20as%20victims.%20I%20commend%20the%20career%20prosecutors%20of%20this%20Office%20for%20bringing%20this%20important%20case%20to%20a%20just%20conclusion.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EStatement%20of%20U.S.%20Attorney%20Damian%20Williams%20on%20the%20conviction%20of%20Darius%20Paduch%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%94%97%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOnAFAhl6tp%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOnAFAhl6tp%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcT85xCGe4x%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcT85xCGe4x%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20US%20Attorney%20SDNY%20(%40SDNYnews)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSDNYnews%2Fstatus%2F1788289727696711959%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20himself%2C%20the%20doctor%20had%20claimed%20some%20of%20his%20methods%20of%20touching%20patients%20were%20medically%20necessary.%20However%2C%20the%20indictment%20said%20they%20were%20intended%20for%20his%20sexual%20gratification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20verdict%2C%20Mallory%20Allen%2C%20a%20lawyer%20representing%20his%20victims%20said%2C%20''For%20nearly%20twenty%20years%2C%20patients%20who%20trusted%20him%20for%20their%20medical%20care%20and%20treatment%20were%20instead%20brutalized%20by%20his%20degrading%2C%20sexually%20violating%2C%20and%20medically%20unfounded%20acts%20while%20the%20hospitals%20were%20he%20worked%20looked%20the%20other%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20jury%20verdict%20in%20the%20criminal%20case%20affirms%20that%20these%20heinous%20acts%20will%20not%20be%20overlooked%2C%20and%20the%20pending%20civil%20cases%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20institutions%20who%20repeatedly%20prioritized%20profits%20over%20their%20patients%20will%20face%20consequences%20for%20their%20indifference%20in%20ignoring%20years%20of%20complaints%2C''%20Mr%20Allen%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disgraced%20doctor%20who's%20been%20behind%20bars%20since%20his%20April%202023%20arrest%20faces%20up%20to%2060%20years%20imprisonment%20at%20his%20sentencing.%20However%2C%20his%20attorney%20Michael%20Baldassare%C2%A0said%20his%20client%20would%20seek%20to%20appeal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Dr.%20Darius%20Paduch%20has%20maintained%20his%20innocence%20since%20the%20start%20of%20this%20case.%20He%20maintains%20it%20to%20this%20day%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20him.%20We%20will%20be%20filing%20post-trial%20motions%20and%20an%20appeal%20and%20will%20seek%20all%20available%20relief%2C''%20the%20attorney%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715274120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fhuuc3ugo_darius-paduch_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-doctor-convicted-of-sexually-abusing-8-patients-including-minors-5627585%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2055-year-old%20doctor%20was%20found%20guilty%20by%20a%20jury%20Wednesday%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20on%20all%2013%20counts%20he%20faced%20related%20to%20his%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20eight%20patients.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-doctor-convicted-of-sexually-abusing-8-patients-including-minors-5627585%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-doctor-convicted-of-sexually-abusing-8-patients-including-minors-5627585%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-doctor-convicted-of-sexually-abusing-8-patients-including-minors-5627585%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doorcam%20captures%20tornado%20winds%20tearing%20down%20trees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715272257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F068E%2Fproduction%2F_133287610_p0hx26hl.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68980346%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20week%20of%20severe%20storms%20has%20left%20a%20trail%20of%20damage%20and%20flooding%20in%20multiple%20parts%20of%20the%20central%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-us-canada-68980346%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CExactly%20why%20we%20need..%