ther%20Siri%20that%20provides%20delicious%20ice%20creams%20in%20parts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Telangana.%20What%E2%80%99s%20even%20more%20special%20is%20that%20these%20ice-creams%20are%20millet-based%20and%20vegan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Prabu%20Venugopal%2C%20Shashidhar%2C%20Arun%20Prakash%2C%20and%20Bhargav%20%E2%80%94%20started%20%E2%80%98Siri%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345217%2Fbest-ice-cream-parlours-places-mumbai-snowman-taj-icecream-haji-ali-gokul-rustom-naturals-bachelorr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegan%20ice-cream%20%3C%2Fa%3Eparlour%20in%20Trichy%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20change%20the%20definition%20of%20this%20frozen%20dessert%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%20globetrotters%20hailed%20from%20different%20industries%2C%20they%20shared%20a%20common%20thread%20%E2%80%94%20they%20all%20had%20farming%20backgrounds.%20So%20after%20working%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20four%20professionals%20quit%20their%20cushy%20jobs%20and%20returned%20to%20their%20hometowns%20%E2%80%94%20Prabu%20and%20Arun%20to%20Trichy%3B%20Shashidhar%20and%20Bhargav%20to%20Hyderabad%20%E2%80%94%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20pooled%20their%20diverse%20experiences%20in%20hotel%20management%2C%20food%20science%2C%20marketing%20and%20finance%2C%20and%20brainstormed%20ideas%20to%20use%20their%20farmland%20as%20a%20valuable%20resource%20to%20build%20a%20thriving%20food%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassionate%20about%20building%20sustainable%20food%20systems%2C%20they%20zeroed%20in%20on%20growing%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20supergrains%20%E2%80%94%20millets.%20Known%20for%20its%20drought-resistant%20qualities%20and%20nutritional%20benefits%2C%20millet%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20candidate%20to%20promote%20both%20health%20and%20sustainability.%20Their%20effor