0designed%20a%20website%20for%20Deeva%20and%20listed%20the%20most%20buying%20categories%20on%20the%20homepage.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20understood%20that%20my%20customers%20were%20office-going%20women%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2025%20to%2045%20years%20who%20wanted%20to%20wear%20good%20quality%20sarees%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20by%20investing%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%202%2C500.%20I%20started%20sourcing%20more%20such%20sarees%20from%20manufacturers%20and%20advertised%20them%20on%20the%20homepage%20for%20easy%20search%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20sales%2C%20Ankush%20also%20outsourced%20to%20a%20digital%20marketing%20company%20that%20helped%20advertise%20the%20sarees.%20%E2%80%9CSoon%20after%2C%20I%20started%20getting%20sales%20through%20social%20media.%20I%20got%20my%20first%20boost%20in%20April-May%202022%20when%20I%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20in%20one%20day.%20This%20was%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20back%20to%20Himachal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20village%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20established%20a%20multi-crore%20company%20based%20out%20of%20Bangana%20that%20sells%20sarees%20across%20the%20country%20in%2050%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Patola%2C%20Kanjivaram%2C%20Chanderi%2C%20Banarasi%20silk%2C%20and%20Chiffon%20sarees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4mbhbOPt4v%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4mbhbOPt4v%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv