%20multidisciplinary%20services%20to%20children%20who%20have%20cancer%20and%20their%20families%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-4-1714469540-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20of%20Access%20Life%2C%20an%20initiative%20that%20provides%20multidisciplinary%20services%20to%20children%20who%20have%20cancer%20and%20their%20families%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ankeet%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20families%20are%20cared%20for%20well%20here%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20they%20have%20a%20life%20waiting%20for%20them%20back%20in%20their%20respective%20villages.%20What%20happens%20to%20that%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Access%20Life%E2%80%99s%20Emotional%20and%20Psychological%20Support%20(EPS)%20programme%20comes%20in.%20It%20equips%20families%20with%20practical%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20distress%20created%20by%20the%20disease.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20keeping%20the%20children%20engaged%20with%20educational%20sessions%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20out%20on%20school%2C%20and%20teaching%20the%20parents%20new%20skills%20that%20could%20be%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20when%20they%20return%20to%20their%20respective%20hometowns%20after%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20long%20treatment%2C%20the%20duo%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%